              <p style='font-size:16.0pt;font-family:"Verdana";
color:maroon;'>
                ConnectOne Version 4.1 Released...!!
              </p>
              <p style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Garamond";
color:#0070C0;'>
                Following new documents are available in Document Library:-<br/>
                1)  TAN Details for PBKIVV,WRST,RERF,BKES,TSRCT,SSAF<br/>
                2)  Fillable Cash Book Cover Page for PBKIVV,WRST,RERF,BKES,TSRCT,SSAF<br/>
                3)  PBKIVV - Exemption from Registration(Hindi,English)
              </p>
              <br/>
              <img src="http://accountserver.bkinfo.in/news/newsfiles/Continuous_Audit.png"/>
              <p style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Garamond";
color:#0070C0;'>
                <u>18th July, 2012</u> <br/>
                Following new documents are available in Document Library:-<br/>
                1)  New Bank Account Opening Form (English)<br/>
                2)  PAN Card Copy of BKES, TSRCT and SSAF <br/>
                3)  WRST Regitration Certificate under Bombay Public Trust Act <br/>
                4)  BKES Registration under Bombay Public Trust Act<br/>
                5)  RERF Registration under Societies Act<br/>
                6)  Income Tax Exemption Related Documents <br/>
                &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;a) BKES - Sec 10(23)(C)(VI) exemption<br/>
                &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;b) BKES - 80G Exemption<br/>
                &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;c) WRST - Sec 10(23)(C)(VI) exemption<br/>
                &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;d) WRST - 80G Exemption<br/>
                &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;e) PBKIVV - Registration under Sec 12AA<br/>
                &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;f) PBKIVV - Notification under Sec 10(23)(C)(V)<br/>
                7)  New Property Affidavit in English <br/>
                8)  Vehicle Transfer Form - 29, 30 <br/>
                9)  New TDS covering Letter <br/>
                10) Internal Transfer Receipt in Hindi<br/>
                11) New application form for Purchase of Property in Hindi and English<br/>
                12) New Affidavit for Gift of Property in Hindi<br/>
              </p><br/>

