color:#0070C0;'>
                <b>New Financial Year Entries in Connect One  available now!!</b>
              </p>
              <p style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Garamond","sans-serif";
mso-fareast-font-family:"Garamond";mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
color:#0070C0;'>
                <b>
                  Connect One Version 4.0
                  New Features:
                </b><br/>
                • 	Accounting for Financial Year 2012-13 Started. <br/>
                • 	Added Asset Transfer Voucher to transfer assets from one centre to other. <br/>
                • 	Telephone No Specific Bill Payment Capturing and Report.<br/>
                • 	Original / Reset Passwords will now be different for each UID instead of one for all UIDs under one BK Centre .<br/>
                • 	Some Internal Transfer and JV Bugs have been fixed. <br/>
                • 	Centre Specific Information has been made online.<br/>
              </p>
